    <div class="article-teaser">
        From Saturday 27 September 2008, bus route 365 will run 24 hours a day.
        
    </div>



<div class="pull-quote">
        <div class="quote-body">"The 24-hour service on route 365 will provide valuable night time links for residents of Havering"</div>
        <div class="quote-footer">
            <div class="quotee-name">John Barry</div>
            <div class="quotee-job-title">Head of Network Development</div>
        </div>
